orable outing for the organizers of the prestigious AfricaMagic Viewers Choice Awards,AMVCAs, as this year’s edition of the awards ceremony held amid pomp last Saturday night, in Lagos. March 11, 2016 In "Showtime People" Glamour, fashion and style are bound to take the centre stage as the African movie stars and stakeholders gather this evening at the Eko Convention for this year’s edition of the prestigious AfricaMagic Viewers Choice Awards, AMVCAs. March 5, 2016 In "Home Video People"